profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

profile:
Paint Core Finishes is a custom refinishing company. We provide top-notch kitchen cabinet, vanity, woodwork and furniture re-spraying, refinishing and painting services in the GTA.

Reclaim your kitchen cabinets, vanities, and woodwork!

We believe in doing things right the first time. We specialize in the fine art of cabinet refinishing, painting, re-spraying and wood finishing. If you have a tired looking kitchen and are thinking of replacing it, think twice. We have salvaged hundreds of kitchens with our factory finish process. We pride ourselves on producing high quality finishes on all your existing cabinetry, millwork and furniture. By implementing a very thorough preparation, combined with the right application systems, topnotch equipment and coatings we provide amazing results. This is our recipe for success!

Our philosophy is that a refinished kitchen shouldn’t look refinished; it should look like it was bought that way.

www.paintcore.ca

profile:
From the year 1989 Brampton Kitchen & Cabinets Ltd. has been designing and manufacturing Custom Cabinetry, with Custom Kitchens being its flagship service. Brampton Kitchen follows a set of ethical values and professional procedures. We operate with the highest level of integrity and rigidly adhere to the policy of customer service, accountability and skill. We are a credible organization that stands behind its product. 
Extensive experience of several years and expertise of best artisans and craftsmen, we create designs that stand out. Be it your Kitchen, Bathroom, Vanity, Entertainment Unit, Bar or Walk-in Closet we have the skills to meet your every need. Our thorough knowledge of our trade is our biggest asset. We learn about your lifestyle while working alongside with you, so as to tailor your kitchen or cabinetry according to your specifications. From Planning to Designing to Manufacturing, we make sure you love every step along the way. We educate you about the industry, current trends and styles so that you make an informed decision.  We can turn your dream into reality without having to compromise on budget or quality.

THE KITCHEN IS THE FOCAL POINT OF ANY HOME.
It serves as a nucleus of food preparation, an informal meeting place and often has a unique look to set it apart from the other rooms in your home. 
If you are considering a new kitchen or an upgrade, Marca can help you with a variety of kitchen designs and ideas.
We also design and build for all cabinetry and millwork required throughout the home.

Our design team will assist you to create a unique design specifically tailored to achieve the exact look you are envisioning. 
From material selections to colours we will be there to provide you with plenty of options to ensure we capture the design perfectly. 
As we are building cabinets of beauty and functionality we believe it is very important to match this with top of the line hardware, which we offer a lifetime warranty on.

Give us a call - (416) 688-3447

profile:
With our painter's techniques and attention to detail, we can make your home and/or business look and feel more like your own. 

We are residential and commercial house painters painting in Pickering, Ajax, Scarborough and the greater Toronto area. We also serve the York and Durham regions to as far north as Aurora.

Our house painting services include general painting, plaster repair, wallpaper and wallcovering installation and removal, decorative painting, and faux finishes. We also offer more speciality services listed under the "Service Details" section below. 

Founded by award-winning decorator Walter Schellenberg in 1989, Decorating with a Difference has had the privilege of working in many of the finest homes in all of Toronto and the GTA, and has now expanded locally with the addition of his sons joining the business, and the partnerships he has created over the years. 

If you are interested in working with us to start or complete your project, please contact us and we'll respond as soon as possible, we look forward to working with you!

Note: 
In an effort to respond quicker, we have set up an automated estimate booking system on our website that will allow you the client, to choose the date that works best for you to have your project quote done in person. 

The system instantly confirms the appointment once you select the date so there is no need to wait for a call. That way you don't have to wait around for a reply, and we can keep painting without checking our phone.
products: We work with any brand of paint, varnish, stain, wallpaper or wallcovering that is required for your project. From low VOC paint for clearer air, to oil paint for that tough smooth finish used on doors and kitchen cabinets. We can even install grass cloth or silk wallcoverings.
services: General Painting, Wallpaper/ Wallcovering (installation & removal), Decorative Painting, Plaster Repair, Faux Finishes, & Murals.
brands: We work with Benjamin Moore, Sherwin-Williams, Behr, and Farrow & Ball to name a few.

Established in 2015, we are a fast growing, full service, detail-oriented custom cabinetry company trusted by customers in the Greater Toronto Area.

Fantasy Kitchen specializes in offering top-quality custom kitchen cabinets in Markham. We are passionate about enhancing the beauty and functionality of your home. As the most trusted cabinet manufacturer in GTA, we craft and install custom bathroom vanities in Richmond Hill.

Our goal is to exceed your expectations on every project, regardless of size. We have a team of skilled craftsmen for designing and installing custom wall units in Markham. Whether you need custom kitchen cabinets, bathroom vanity, walk-in closet, or home bar, we can customize cabinetry to suit your taste, style, and budget. Our team can also install custom wall units in Richmond Hill homes and commercial spaces. As a full-service cabinetry installer, we can make your home more stylish, comfortable, and spacious.

When it comes to kitchen cabinets and bathroom vanities, you need products that can withstand temperature fluctuations due to heat from stoves and ovens and moisture from showers, sinks, and dishwashers.

We focus on using the highest quality material and durable fixtures that can stand the test of time. Our process involves taking accurate measurements and understanding your vision to deliver tailored solutions. When we install custom bathroom vanities in Vaughan, we make sure to provide you a product that complements the size and style of your space.

We strive to turn your bathroom into a sanctuary. When we work on any project, our designers consider aesthetics, as well as functionality. Our experts will not only help you choose the right cabinetry material but can also guide you to select the best hardware and finishes that look phenomenal and can stand up to the challenges of a bathroom or kitchen environment. Our services include:

• Kitchen & Bathroom Design Consultation
• Custom Cabinets Manufacturer
• Kitchen Cabinetry Installation
• Bathroom Vanity Installation
• Walk-In Closet Installation
• Home Bar & Pantry
• And More!

At Fantasy Kitchen, we take great pride in our workmanship. From crafting custom Kitchen cabinets in Markham to installing bathroom vanities in Richmond Hill, we provide a wide range of superior quality products and spectacular installation services for almost every budget and style. We always respect your time and consider your ideas to ensure that the project is completed as per your requirements and expectations. We provide you the freedom to choose from our wide assortment of premium materials. In addition to this, we always provide accurate project quote to keep you informed. The cabinets we install provide a great storage solution to provide you an organized and attractive-looking space.
